{"tid":2367013,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"澳洲煤企：中國從其他國家買貴貨　最後到手還是澳洲煤","createTime":"2021-01-15T04:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T05:24:34.000Z","uid":28114,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"477182fdfee945ae9ca4b97c89eb2790c2031e11","tid":2367013,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T04:10:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/china-still-indirectly-buying-australian-coal-producer-revealed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.com.au%2Flanguage%2Fcantonese%2Fzh-hant%2Fchina-still-indirectly-buying-australian-coal-producer-revealed&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFtVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=e3c45f02\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/china-still-indirectly-buying-australian-coal-producer-revealed</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://sl.sbs.com.au/public/image/file/04f66515-4c84-41af-8161-0c3e667650d0/crop/16x9_large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsl.sbs.com.au%2Fpublic%2Fimage%2Ffile%2F04f66515-4c84-41af-8161-0c3e667650d0%2Fcrop%2F16x9_large&h=d46dd0b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新聞公司報道，澳洲煤炭上市公司Whitehaven Coal昨日（1月14日）發表12月季度報告，表示中國的貿易限制措施，改變了海運煤炭貿易的流向。該公司說：「中國已用更高成本購入俄羅斯、印尼、南非等國家的煤炭，來取代其國內生產。」<br />\n<br />\n澳洲煤炭不再運到中國，正尋找其他地方的客戶，包括印度、巴基斯坦和中東。傳統上，送到這些市場的貿易煤炭，最終目的地是中國。<br />\n<br />\n中國的禁令，使一批載滿煤炭的船隻在中國沿海地區無法卸貨，澳洲聯邦政府正尋求世界貿易組織介入。<br />\n<br />\nWhitehaven說，中國買家的缺席，壓低了用作煉鋼的澳洲冶金煤的價格，但該公司在印度、日本、南韓和台灣的冶金煤市場，受益於經濟刺激措施下有所增長。<br />\n<br />\n「印度在年中的抗疫封城措施後，（對冶金煤的）需求強烈反彈，繼續成為Whitehaven冶金煤一個成長中的市場。」<br />\n<br />\n該公司行政總裁Paul Flynn說，中國禁令對Whitehaven的銷售影響甚微，「我們如之前一樣，仍然出售同一噸數（的煤炭）給同一批客戶。」<br />\n<br />\n我們看到，（澳洲市場上）很多以往售賣煤炭給中國的參與者，轉而出售給以往沒有的市場，而中國在實施禁令期間，要向非傳統的來源購入煤炭，以滿足其需要。<br />\n<br />\n「我沒聽見過（中國進口澳洲煤炭）配額改變的消息。恰恰相反，似乎有更多煽動言論顯示中國更堅決不買澳洲煤炭。不過，正如我之前所說，最終真的對我們的沒多少影響。」<br />\n<br />\n至於用來發電的動力煤方面，Whitehaven說其需求繼續由去年8月的低位上升，因為亞洲供應減少加上對能源需求上升。<br />\n<br />\n另外，《雪梨晨鋒報》引述澳洲礦業人士報道，中國的鋼鐵商告訴他們，他們正遊說中國政府放寬進口禁令，但不成功。<br />\n<br />\n一名消息人士說：「中國鋼鐵業遊說政府，說他們需要澳洲產品，因為他們需要那種數量和質量，來生產可樂（罐）以至鋼鐵（等製品）。」"},{"pid":"76eca0d042bb5cb6b92874578e92a6d9a0cb3b42","tid":2367013,"uid":28114,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T04:12:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/183416_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F183416_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=18029139&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b14378226ee721caf804821c420c03309aa559b","tid":2367013,"uid":40272,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T04:12:08.000Z","msg":"錢大把 習種既面子不可丟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e1bebb4a0575ac27816b3694f450ee59330a586","tid":2367013,"uid":100772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T04:14:08.000Z","msg":"佢想買返都高價賣返比佢"},{"pid":"6f1a094f942e40697615da46a914d6818d8567a5","tid":2367013,"uid":10471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T04:16:02.000Z","msg":"促進世界經濟"},{"pid":"c47853af8cf6f8bf25c9cbf5bd1bd4811545b696","tid":2367013,"uid":34804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T04:16:24.000Z","msg":"轉口可以增加全球貿易經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78cbbddec47fb83fae2269bd6ac9fe678e4dba56","tid":2367013,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c47853af8cf6f8bf25c9cbf5bd1bd4811545b696","tid":2367013,"uid":34804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T04:16:24.000Z","msg":"轉口可以增加全球貿易經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T04:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj